_sText:
This map was a one day job as a small break from a large surf map currently in the making.

Fun aspects are incorporated, including speeding trains, a large glass panel with deadly boulders and deadlier weapons, and a ridiculously large drop.

This is my first attempt at CS:S mapping, although I've mapped for GMod for a while now, constructive criticism is appreciated, although I really couldn't care less if you want to flame me.

Keep it cool, guys.
Splambob.
